"Note: Hourly Schedule"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Pull Side A (HubSpot)\n\nhubspot — `search` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Diff the Two Systems · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,250],"id":"818930b1-fac1-c6b1-85c0-3e116e18122c","name":"Note: Pull Side A (HubSpot)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Pull Side B (Notion)\n\nnotion — `getAll` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Diff the Two Systems · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,790],"id":"827e0c56-ab4a-7ed1-4e1b-781503f8032f","name":"Note: Pull Side B (Notion)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Diff the Two Systems\n\nDiffs two streams by key into 4 lanes: only-in-A, same, different, only-in-B — the heart of the sync.\n\nPorts: ①→ Create Missing in Notion · ②→ Count In-Sync Rows · ③→ Apply Updates to Notion · ④→ Backfill into HubSpot","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,520],"id":"aaf616c3-1218-399e-8444-8514fa5511ad","name":"Note: Diff the Two Systems"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Create Missing in Notion\n\nnotion — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Gather Sync Results · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1938,-80],"id":"0b97286d-45b1-33f8-e6e6-5d40b90e74e4","name":"Note: Create Missing in Notion"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Count In-Sync Rows\n\nCollapses all items into a single summary item (for counts and run stats).\n\nNext: Gather Sync Results","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2262,340],"id":"8d72228f-28cc-9096-fc36-32a1cda9d78c","name":"Note: Count In-Sync Rows"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Apply Updates to Notion\n\nnotion — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Gather Sync Results · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2586,760],"id":"e07deebe-d8b4-90bf-7f74-80828e9959cc","name":"Note: Apply Updates to Notion"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Backfill into HubSpot\n\nhubspot — `contact` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Gather Sync Results · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2910,1180],"id":"bce55ce2-ffcf-c90d-45a5-f584d8acd770","name":"Note: Backfill into HubSpot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Gather Sync Results\n\nRejoins 4 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.\n\nNext: Serialize Run Output (CSV)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,520],"id":"206aacf0-7a87-862b-20f2-caa7ec117859","name":"Note: Gather Sync Results"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Serialize Run Output (CSV)\n\nSerializes items to a CSV binary file.\n\nNext: Archive Row Snapshot","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4530,520],"id":"6728eba0-e04d-3484-0fab-9ec664256e85","name":"Note: Serialize Run Output (CSV)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Archive Row Snapshot\n\nnotion — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Fingerprint for Idempotency · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4854,520],"id":"e5290ce0-9231-eac1-d762-2af848fe59d4","name":"Note: Archive Row Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fingerprint for Idempotency\n\nCustom JavaScript: Build a stable idempotency key per job (djb2 hash, no deps)\n\nNext: Drop Already-Processed Items","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5178,520],"id":"888d31f8-2859-7f22-e97e-b9939c654cb3","name":"Note: Fingerprint for Idempotency"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Drop Already-Processed Items\n\nCross-execution dedupe: remembers keys it has processed before and drops repeats — the idempotency guard.\n\nNext: Stamp Completion Time","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5502,520],"id":"4c6dd9d3-df1f-b80c-c46b-3470899bca0e","name":"Note: Drop Already-Processed Items"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Completion Time\n\nStamps `completedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Persist Run Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5826,520],"id":"19349890-13ba-ec14-730f-e2fe2db0f7d1","name":"Note: Stamp Completion Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Persist Run Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Load Previous Snapshot","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6150,520],"id":"57d7a696-e9f5-bdaf-932a-b540d9d63f3a","name":"Note: Persist Run Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Load Previous Snapshot\n\ngoogleSheets — `read` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Compute Drift vs Snapshot · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6474,520],"id":"ce31944b-b1b6-b534-2227-e6395de128c8","name":"Note: Load Previous Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Compute Drift vs Snapshot\n\nCustom JavaScript: Compare current metrics with the previous snapshot\n\nNext: Enrich with Reference Data","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6798,520],"id":"08f4cce4-138e-3f14-87fc-2fcdc578df2a","name":"Note: Compute Drift vs Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Enrich with Reference Data\n\nGET https://enrichment.example.com/v2/lookup — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nPorts: ①→ Fold In Enrichment Fields · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7122,520],"id":"f9a64a73-6857-0801-d9e7-040e4922dccf","name":"Note: Enrich with Reference Data"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fold In Enrichment Fields\n\nShapes the item: writes `enrichedAt`, `enrichmentSource`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7446,520],"id":"6d175d93-09a1-8362-e2f2-11f3fd967a2c","name":"Note: Fold In Enrichment Fields"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow\n\nDelegates to a reusable sub-workflow (single-responsibility building block) and waits for its result.\n\nPorts: ①→ Record Sub-workflow Result · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7770,520],"id":"092f97a8-8afc-b6c9-7faa-cc2d8ee3bced","name":"Note: Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Record Sub-workflow Result\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Cap Batch Volume","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8094,520],"id":"0c2f6a97-cf83-1cc9-ad62-f55e08136938","name":"Note: Record Sub-workflow Result"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Cap Batch Volume\n\nCaps the stream at 25 items to protect downstream quotas.\n\nNext: Stamp Processing Time","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8418,520],"id":"dc2ddac8-34fe-b855-5293-adeb1205b75b","name":"Note: Cap Batch Volume"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Processing Time\n\nStamps `processedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Save Execution Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8742,520],"id":"487ad5e0-09eb-e669-0463-e5840146619d","name":"Note: Stamp Processing Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Save Execution Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Sort Jobs Newest First","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[9066,520],"id":"905d38bb-82ff-ae86-3b2f-42c5be324ce9","name":"Note: Save Execution Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Sort Jobs Newest First\n\nOrders items (newest first) so limits and digests pick the most relevant records.\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[9390,520],"id":"eb7ff2a0-c51c-dd20-f76a-43efcf8fba05","name":"Note: Sort Jobs Newest First"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (HubSpot)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[9714,520],"id":"19a12aca-b8e6-d11e-5060-b63e3961e8ef","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (HubSpot)\n\nhubspot — `contact` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Slack · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[10038,520],"id":"9bf9c149-ae8b-06a0-a8db-96b9e1498f06","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (HubSpot)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[10362,520],"id":"1e99baf4-fad1-5487-b42f-00574c8350b2","name":"Note: Send Summary to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Twilio","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[9714,1540],"id":"6040761e-90bf-2418-4d92-5a029b298287","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Twilio\n\ntwilio — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Twilio SID + token","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[10038,1540],"id":"6292659e-7565-9e19-3636-2f6e707173f4","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Twilio"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\nhubspot — `contact` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[10362,1540],"id":"21e9400d-029e-bde2-8cee-d72ae9441e8e","name":"Note: Park in Dead-Letter Queue"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Mirror records between tools with HubSpot and Notion\n\n**Pattern:** Two-System Sync · **Level:** Architect · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nMirror records between tools with HubSpot and Notion. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual integrations is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nHourly Schedule → Pull Side A (HubSpot) → Diff the Two Systems → Create Missing in Notion → Gather Sync Results → Serialize Run Output (CSV) → Archive Row Snapshot → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to two-system sync without manual effort\n- Anyone automating integrations in productivity\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Scales without extra headcount\n- Has retries and error handling built in\n- Keeps your systems in sync\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: API key / bearer for the target API; Google OAuth2 / service account; HubSpot private-app token; Notion integration token; Slack OAuth2; Twilio SID + token.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"789f9f93-ceb8-5d75-5803-fcf3699cd45b","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Failures are also parked in a dead-letter queue for replay. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-620],"id":"13c76526-a918-05c7-42a8-7714f5048ce9","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🧹 Data quality\n\nDedupe/diff steps make re-runs safe: the same input twice will not create duplicate records. If you change the key fields, clear n8n's dedupe memory (node → 'Clear stored keys') before the next run.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-620],"id":"bbe6797c-cbd6-deb7-7b27-6d58751d8bbf","name":"🧹 Data quality"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your integrations process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-620],"id":"c2af0750-7500-e2e5-116f-4a116d6027a2","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Hourly Schedule":{"main":[[{"node":"Pull Side A (HubSpot)","type":"main","index":0},{"node":"Pull Side B (Notion)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Pull Side A (HubSpot)":{"main":[[{"node":"Diff the Two Systems","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Pull Side B (Notion)":{"main":[[{"node":"Diff the Two Systems","type":"main","index":1}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Diff the Two Systems":{"main":[[{"node":"Create Missing in Notion","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Count In-Sync Rows","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Apply Updates to Notion","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Backfill into HubSpot","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Create Missing in Notion":{"main":[[{"node":"Gather Sync Results","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Count In-Sync Rows":{"main":[[{"node":"Gather Sync Results","type":"main","index":1}]]},"Apply Updates to Notion":{"main":[[{"node":"Gather Sync Results","type":"main","index":2}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Backfill into HubSpot":{"main":[[{"node":"Gather Sync Results","type":"main","index":3}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Gather Sync Results":{"main":[[{"node":"Serialize Run Output (CSV)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Serialize Run Output (CSV)":{"main":[[{"node":"Archive Row Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Archive Row Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Fingerprint for Idempotency","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fingerprint for Idempotency":{"main":[[{"node":"Drop Already-Processed Items","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Drop Already-Processed Items":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp Completion Time","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp Completion Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Persist Run Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Persist Run Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Load Previous Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Load Previous Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Compute Drift vs Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Compute Drift vs Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Enrich with Reference Data","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Enrich with Reference Data":{"main":[[{"node":"Fold In Enrichment Fields","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fold In Enrichment Fields":{"main":[[{"node":"Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow":{"main":[[{"node":"Record Sub-workflow Result","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Record Sub-workflow Result":{"main":[[{"node":"Cap Batch Volume","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Cap Batch Volume":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp Processing Time","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp Processing Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Save Execution Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Save Execution Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Sort Jobs Newest First","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Sort Jobs Newest First":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (HubSpot)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (HubSpot)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Slack","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Twilio","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Escalate Failure to Twilio":{"main":[[{"node":"Park in Dead-Letter Queue","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Slack":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"81957040-c50b-4b10-b921-792678f39e57","id":"FDX05884"}